  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cut down hordes of enemies <strong>automatically</strong> in <strong>Nomad Idle</strong>, a spin-off of <i>Nomad Survival</i>. Engage in an expansive storyline, make impactful decisions, and grow stronger through various gameplay features that gradually unlock as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/bad3d84c14b7c51be952b4fe1dcb3ed3.poster.avif?t=1767920045\" width=664 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/bad3d84c14b7c51be952b4fe1dcb3ed3.webm?t=1767920045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/bad3d84c14b7c51be952b4fe1dcb3ed3.mp4?t=1767920045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nomad Idle</strong> is an idle game with a defined end and is not designed to be endless. However, that does not mean the game is short or lacks depth. In <strong>Nomad Idle</strong>, you can expect to have access to the following as you play through the game and unlock more features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Level up and earn Stat Points</strong> which may be distributed within 7 unique Stats, allowing you to create a build.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Discover, craft, and upgrade Equipment</strong> in order to make yourself stronger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Conjure Summons</strong> to aid you in battle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Select Passive Skills to be automatically used in battle</strong>, further defining your build. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Choose a Character,</strong> defining your active abilities and special perks for your playthrough.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/a05070ede7ef7934b3907ac4bb360fa1.poster.avif?t=1767920045\" width=664 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/a05070ede7ef7934b3907ac4bb360fa1.webm?t=1767920045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/a05070ede7ef7934b3907ac4bb360fa1.mp4?t=1767920045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nomad Idle</strong> is an <strong>idle game</strong>, meaning that it mostly <strong>plays on its own</strong>. Your character moves and attacks enemies all on their own, but it <strong>can be played actively</strong> by making use of character-specific skills and abilities. Playing actively in this way is <strong>entirely optional</strong> and not mandatory, but can be effective in speeding up your progress or help you overcome challenges.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cut down hordes of enemies <strong>automatically</strong> in <strong>Nomad Idle</strong>, a spin-off of <i>Nomad Survival</i>. Engage in an expansive storyline, make impactful decisions, and grow stronger through various gameplay features that gradually unlock as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/bad3d84c14b7c51be952b4fe1dcb3ed3.poster.avif?t=1767920045\" width=664 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/bad3d84c14b7c51be952b4fe1dcb3ed3.webm?t=1767920045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/bad3d84c14b7c51be952b4fe1dcb3ed3.mp4?t=1767920045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nomad Idle</strong> is an idle game with a defined end and is not designed to be endless. However, that does not mean the game is short or lacks depth. In <strong>Nomad Idle</strong>, you can expect to have access to the following as you play through the game and unlock more features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Level up and earn Stat Points</strong> which may be distributed within 7 unique Stats, allowing you to create a build.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Discover, craft, and upgrade Equipment</strong> in order to make yourself stronger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Conjure Summons</strong> to aid you in battle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Select Passive Skills to be automatically used in battle</strong>, further defining your build. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Choose a Character,</strong> defining your active abilities and special perks for your playthrough.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/a05070ede7ef7934b3907ac4bb360fa1.poster.avif?t=1767920045\" width=664 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/a05070ede7ef7934b3907ac4bb360fa1.webm?t=1767920045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042190/extras/a05070ede7ef7934b3907ac4bb360fa1.mp4?t=1767920045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nomad Idle</strong> is an <strong>idle game</strong>, meaning that it mostly <strong>plays on its own</strong>. Your character moves and attacks enemies all on their own, but it <strong>can be played actively</strong> by making use of character-specific skills and abilities. Playing actively in this way is <strong>entirely optional</strong> and not mandatory, but can be effective in speeding up your progress or help you overcome challenges.</p>",
